bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Player 1 has been assigned the Role Card - Generalist

[wave]Special Ability[/wave] - The Generalist has an additional action to support their team, and may take 5 actions per turn instead of 4.

[wave]Leveraging your Role[/wave] - The Generalist stays true to its name, and should focus on aiding your team wherever needed.  This can be in the form of using an extra movement to reach trouble areas faster, removing additional cubes off of dangerous cities, or trading additional cards to other Roles.

Work closely together with other players and save the world from the Pandemic!

Have fun :)
"
autowrap_mode = 2

